</div>

<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    <p>Cookies are files saved on your phone, tablet or computer when you visit a website.</p>
    <p>We use cookies to store information about how you use the Vehicle Operator Licensing website, such as the pages you visit.</p>
</div>

<div class="cookie-settings__form-wrapper">
